PN,41601
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1776246948
OL,3,CFormer Treloars pupils infected in
OL,4,Cblood scandal to receive more
OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,FFormer Treloar School pupils who were
OL,8,Finfected with HIV and hepatitis are
OL,9,Fset to receive thousands of pounds
OL,10,Fmore in compensation after a patient
OL,11,Fwarned a previous offer was "way off
OL,12,Fthe mark".
OL,14,FCabinet Office minister Nick Thomas-
OL,15,FSymonds told the Commons that
OL,16,Fcompensation "must reflect and embody"
OL,17,Finfected patients' experiences "if it
OL,18,Fis to truly deliver justice".
OL,26,@sD@]OUtD@IO]xD@NOUxD@fO]yD@`OUzD@\O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1776246948
OL,3,CFormer Treloars pupils infected in
OL,4,Cblood scandal to receive more
OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,FThe Lord Mayor Treloar College in
OL,8,FHampshire offered specialist care for
OL,9,Fchildren with haemophilia during the
OL,10,F1970s and 1980s, and pupils undergoing
OL,11,Ftreatment for the disorder were
OL,12,Fexperimented on without their
OL,13,Fknowledge by clinicians.
OL,15,FThey were previously offered a one-off
OL,16,F#15,000 payment on top of the ongoing
OL,17,Fsupport, with a #10,000 award
OL,18,Favailable for others in similar, less
OL,19,Fnotorious cases.But this figure is set
OL,20,Fto rise to #60,000.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1776246948
OL,3,CFormer Treloars pupils infected in
OL,4,Cblood scandal to receive more
OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,F"I know the matter of unethical
OL,8,Fresearch is of particular concern to
OL,9,Fmembers across the House and is one of
OL,10,Fthe most shocking aspects of this
OL,11,Fscandal," Mr Thomas-Symonds said,
OL,12,Ffollowing a consultation on the
OL,13,Farrangements.
OL,15,F"We heard that the existing approach
OL,16,Fmay not have compensated everyone who
OL,17,Fsuffered this wrongdoing, so first, we
OL,18,Fhave changed the scope of this award
OL,19,Fso that anyone treated in the UK for a
OL,20,Fbleeding disorder in 1985 or earlier
OL,21,Fwill receive further compensation.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@IO]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1776246948
OL,3,CFormer Treloars pupils infected in
OL,4,Cblood scandal to receive more
OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,F"It was also clear from the
OL,8,Fconsultation responses that the amount
OL,9,Foffered does not reflect the harm done.
OL,11,F"I say today to the House, we will
OL,12,Fincrease the unethical research
OL,13,Fawards. This includes increasing the
OL,14,F#25,000 for those who attended Treloar
OL,15,FSchool to #60,000 as well as
OL,16,Fintroducing a new unethical research
OL,17,Faward for those treated elsewhere for
OL,18,Fa bleeding disorder during childhood
OL,19,Fat a rate of #45,000.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1776246948
OL,3,CFormer Treloars pupils infected in
OL,4,Cblood scandal to receive more
OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,F"We're also tripling the award for
OL,8,Fthose treated for a bleeding disorder
OL,9,Fin adulthood to #30,000."
OL,11,FMore than 30,000 people throughout the
OL,12,FUK were infected with HIV and
OL,13,Fhepatitis C after they were given
OL,14,Fcontaminated blood and blood products
OL,15,Fbetween the 1970s and early 1990s.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@YO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1776246948
OL,3,CFormer Treloars pupils infected in
OL,4,Cblood scandal to receive more
OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,FAs part of his announcement, the
OL,8,Fminister also told MPs that infected
OL,9,Fpeople "who can show they either had a
OL,10,Fjob offer or recently started a job
OL,11,Fwhere the salary was higher than the
OL,12,Fmedian salary, but had their progress
OL,13,Fimpeded by their infection" would
OL,14,Freceive the offer of a #60,000 lump
OL,15,Fsum on top of the core award.
OL,26,@qD@HOUuD@[O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1776246948
OL,3,CFormer Treloars pupils infected in
OL,4,Cblood scandal to receive more
OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,FSetting out the Government's response
OL,8,Fto the consultation, Mr Thomas-Symonds
OL,9,Fhad earlier said: "The community were
OL,10,Fclear that the scheme must do more to
OL,11,Frecognise people's individual
OL,12,Fexperiences and compensate them fairly
OL,13,Fin a way that minimises the
OL,14,Fadministrative burden placed upon
OL,15,Fthose who have been harmed, minimises
OL,16,Fthe demand for evidence and maintains
OL,17,Fthe delivery of tariff-based
OL,18,Fcompensation, and those requirements
OL,19,Funderpin the changes.
OL,26,@qD@SOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1776246948
OL,3,CFormer Treloars pupils infected in
OL,4,Cblood scandal to receive more
OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,F"For infected people, the changes will
OL,8,Fincrease the amount of core
OL,9,Fcompensation available and increase
OL,10,Fthe options available for
OL,11,Fsupplementary compensation awards.
OL,13,F"For affected people, additional core
OL,14,Fcompensation will be available to
OL,15,Fthose eligible."
OL,17,FMore than #2 billion has been paid in
OL,18,Fcompensation to victims of the
OL,19,Finfected blood scandal, and as of
OL,20,FApril 7, 3,273 people had received a
OL,21,Fpayment offer.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUwD@PO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1776246948
OL,3,CFormer Treloars pupils infected in
OL,4,Cblood scandal to receive more
OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,FGary Webster, who was infected with
OL,8,FHIV and hepatitis C when he attend
OL,9,FTreloar's in the 1970s and 80s,
OL,10,Fearlier this year said that a payment
OL,11,Foffer of #25,000 was "way off the
OL,12,Fmark".
OL,14,FHe said of the 122 haemophiliac boys
OL,15,Fwho attended the college, more than 80
OL,16,Fare now dead.
OL,26,@sD@VOUtD@EO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1776246948
OL,3,CFormer Treloars pupils infected in
OL,4,Cblood scandal to receive more
OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,FReacting to the latest announcement,
OL,8,FMr Webster said: "I'm glad they have
OL,9,Flistened and I'm glad they have
OL,10,Fincluded all haemophiliacs throughout
OL,11,Fthe UK.
OL,13,F"It's an increase from the #25,000 but
OL,14,Fis #60,000 enough for a life?
OL,16,F"It's better but I'm not jumping up
OL,17,Fand down.
OL,19,F"Everyone admits it was shocking and
OL,20,Fthe minister there said it should
OL,21,Fnever happen again."
OL,26,@pD@ROUuD@AOUxD@AOU{D@AOU}D@TO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1776246948
OL,3,CFormer Treloars pupils infected in
OL,4,Cblood scandal to receive more
OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FThe Government also announced it plans
OL,13,Fto increase core injury awards for
OL,14,Fparents whose child died before they
OL,15,Fturned 18, as well as bereaved
OL,16,Fpartners and children and siblings
OL,17,Faffected under the age of 18.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1776246948
OL,3,CFormer Treloars pupils infected in
OL,4,Cblood scandal to receive more
OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,FLabour MP Ruth Cadbury called for this
OL,8,Fenhanced core injury payment to be
OL,9,Fextended to parents whose children
OL,10,Fdied over the age of 18, but had no
OL,11,Fpartner or children of their own.
OL,13,FThe Brentford and Isleworth MP said:
OL,14,F"For many people infected by HIV in
OL,15,Fthe 1980s, fear, stigma and poor
OL,16,Fhealth meant the role of their
OL,17,Fparents, such as my constituents,
OL,18,Fdidn't meaningfully change after their
OL,19,Fchild turned 18."
OL,26,@vD@AOU{D@QO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1776246948
OL,3,CFormer Treloars pupils infected in
OL,4,Cblood scandal to receive more
OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,FResponding, Mr Thomas-Symonds said she
OL,8,Fwas right to talk about the "terrible
OL,9,Fsocial stigma" suffered, and that he
OL,10,Fhopes the scheme does "reflect" that.
OL,12,FThe minister told MPs that the
OL,13,Fnecessary legislation to implement
OL,14,Fchanges to the infected blood
OL,15,Fcompensation scheme will be brought
OL,16,Fforward "as soon as possible".
OL,26,@pD@]OUqD@NO]rD@WOUrD@_O]xD@IOUxD@]O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1776246948
OL,3,CFormer Treloars pupils infected in
OL,4,Cblood scandal to receive more
OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,FLiberal Democrat Cabinet Office
OL,8,Fspokesperson Lisa Smart said that
OL,9,Fthere are people who "continue to feel
OL,10,Fthat the scheme does not go far
OL,11,Fenough", in particular those who feel
OL,12,Fit should "investigate more potential
OL,13,Fconditions".
OL,15,FShe also criticised the "shameful"
OL,16,Fdelay in passing the Hillsborough Law,
OL,17,Fwhich is set to introduce a statutory
OL,18,Fduty for public authorities to tell
OL,19,Fthe truth, saying that victims "should
OL,20,Fnot be made to wait any longer".
OL,26,@qD@VOUsD@GO]tD@KOUuD@KO]wD@YOUwD@bO]{D@
OL,26,A`OU|D@_O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G14/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
